summary: Just a simple home next to Riverwood. Designed for Hunter characters.
descriptionHtml:
Please cut me some slack, this is my first mod. I tried my best to make it big but simple.

Features:
-Mounted trophy heads
-Small collection of skulls
-Two-roomed basement
-Cooking pot
-Riverside and creekside position
-Porch
-River and creek bridge
-Close to riverwood

I hope that whoever actually downloads this will be satisfied!
author: TheDarkWolf45
